subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: Provision of acess to financial servicesto 2,000 small, medium and large scale women entrepreneurs (SMLEs) for investment; provide acess and capacity development (technical and entrepreneurship enhancement) services to 2,000 women entrepreneurs (SMLEs); Increase access to sustained business development services to 2,000 growth oriented women SMLEs; Enhance investment culture among 1,000 women entrepreneurs to increase wealth; and Improved Governments’ regulatory, policy and support environment for small, medium and large enterprises making it conducive for women entrepreneurs to increase their productivity, competitiveness and access to wider markets
subproject.gender code: Gender Equality as a principal objective
